criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 20 years;

          -  Screened for GDM during 24-32 weeks of gestation;

          -  With fasting blood samples collected before 20 weeks of gestation (only for nested
             case-control subjects).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of a diagnosis of diabetes or gestational diabetes;

          -  History of receiving pharmacological treatment known to affect glucose metabolism;

          -  Clinically significant neurological, endocrinological or other systemic diseases and
             multiple pregnancies.
